OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1772193711
OL,3,CSchool bus service set to be axed in
OL,4,CDumfries and Galloway
OL,6,FA school bus service in Dumfries and
OL,7,FGalloway is set to be axed leaving up
OL,8,Fto 200 pupils at risk of not having
OL,9,Fsuitable transport to get to school.
OL,11,FParents of non-catchment pupils at
OL,12,FWallace Hall Academy in Thornhill now
OL,13,Fsay they will have to try and find
OL,14,Falternative arrangements to ensure
OL,15,Fthat their children can make it to
OL,16,Fschool.
OL,18,FThere are currently two buses that run
OL,19,Ffrom Dumfries to the school in
OL,20,FThornhill with one of those now set to
OL,21,Fbe scrapped.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
