PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1772193711
OL,3,CSchool bus service set to be axed in
OL,4,CDumfries and Galloway
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Border, Laura Keenan
OL,7,Fwho is the Chair of the parent council
OL,8,Fat Wallace Hall Academy said: "We went
OL,9,Fthrough all this and we were left in
OL,10,Fchaos and we got it sorted out where
OL,11,Fthe buses had been brought back up to,
OL,12,Fwhere there were adequate provision,
OL,13,Fand we thought that was it.
OL,15,F"We thought the job was done, everyone
OL,16,Fwas happy and we were certainly happy.
OL,18,F"We got all the kids to school,
OL,19,Feverything's fine and then for this to
OL,20,Fhappen again, I just thought what are
OL,21,Fthey thinking of.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1772193711
OL,3,CSchool bus service set to be axed in
OL,4,CDumfries and Galloway
OL,6,F"It is supposed to provide adequate
OL,7,Ftransport where there's a need, not
OL,8,Fdictate where people are and aren't
OL,9,Fallowed to go."
OL,11,FAround half of the pupils enrolled at
OL,12,Fthe school at now potentially without
OL,13,Fsuitable transport from July.
OL,15,FJames Driscoll's son was recently left
OL,16,Fat the roadside when the school bus
OL,17,Fwas too busy to pick him up.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
