PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1772193711
OL,3,CSchool bus service set to be axed in
OL,4,CDumfries and Galloway
OL,6,FJames said: "If he was to be left at
OL,7,Fthe bus stop, the chances are we're
OL,8,Fgoing to have to then find
OL,9,Farrangements to get him to school.
OL,11,F"That that's not something that can be
OL,12,Fdone easily. Because both his parents
OL,13,Fwork full time now.
OL,15,F"This is only the second village and
OL,16,Fthe bus has another 11 miles to go
OL,17,Ffrom here. It is something that is
OL,18,Fgoing to have a massive impacts on the
OL,19,Fschool."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/4
